cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use STFU.md in research, benchmarks, or production deployments, please cite it as below."
title: "STFU.md — Shut The Flip Up"
abstract: "A 1.5 KB single-file system prompt that compresses AI coding-agent prose output by 77–87% across 5 production agent CLIs (Claude Code, Google Gemini, Factory Droid, Pi Coding Agent, Cursor Agent) at 100% compliance with hard prompt-shape caps (v0.13.1 5-agent × 5-prompt re-bench). Inspired by caveman (Brussee, 2026); diverges by replacing the caveman persona with a senior-engineer register."
type: software
